itemDescription: British midwife, nurse and nursing administrator

wikipedia_page.main: Maude Storey, CBE, FRCN (24 March 1930 – 29 March 2003) was a British nurse, nursing administrator  and writer, as well as President of the Royal College of Nursing from 1988 to 1990.

response: *Maude Storey (1930–2003), British nurse, nursing administrator and writer, as well as President of the Royal College of Nursing from 1988 to 1990
*Miss Maude Storey, Registrar and Chief Executive, U.K. Central Council for Nursing Midwifery and Health Visiting.
